### Document Portal — runnable request collection
### Open in VS Code (REST Client extension) or JetBrains HTTP client.
### Set the two variables below, then click "Send Request" above each block.

@baseUrl = http://192.168.80.52:2311
@apiKey = PASTE_YOUR_API_KEY_HERE
@reference = 324991

########################################################################
# 1. COLLECTION PORTAL API
########################################################################

### 1.1 Generate all links for a case
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/document-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Theresa Topp",
  "reference": "{{reference}}"
}

### 1.2 List ALL links for a case
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/document-requests?reference={{reference}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 1.3 List only links that have an uploaded document
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/document-requests?reference={{reference}}&uploaded_only=true
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 1.4 List only submitted links
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/document-requests?reference={{reference}}&status=submitted
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 1.5 List only pending (still-open) links
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/document-requests?reference={{reference}}&status=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

########################################################################
# 2. DOCUMENTS API (read)
########################################################################

### 2.1 List documents for a case
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/documents?owner_ref={{reference}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 2.2 List documents filtered by type
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/documents?owner_ref={{reference}}&document_type=immigration_status
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 2.3 Get one document (replace the id)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/documents/6f1e3a3d-cf08-4cf9-99c5-170dfc5cb42f
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 2.4 Stream / preview a document file (replace the id)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/documents/6f1e3a3d-cf08-4cf9-99c5-170dfc5cb42f/file
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 2.5 Update a document (replace the id)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v1/documents/6f1e3a3d-cf08-4cf9-99c5-170dfc5cb42f
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document_type": "proof_of_address",
  "metadata": { "note": "reclassified" }
}

### 2.6 OCR text status (replace the id)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/documents/6f1e3a3d-cf08-4cf9-99c5-170dfc5cb42f/text
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

########################################################################
# 3. CLIENT UPLOAD (public, no auth) — replace <token> from a generated link
########################################################################

### 3.1 Upload a file to a link (multipart)
POST {{baseUrl}}/u/{{reference}}/immigration_status/<token>
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----portal

------portal
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="photo.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./photo.png
------portal--

### 3.2 Public inline preview of a stored file (replace the key)
GET {{baseUrl}}/files/<tenant>/{{reference}}/<req>/original__photo.png

########################################################################
# 4. HEALTH / OPS (no auth)
########################################################################

### 4.1 Liveness
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 4.2 DB reachable
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/db

### 4.3 Readiness
GET {{baseUrl}}/ready
